<!DOCTYPE html>
<html  lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="keywords" content="elderly, granny, old, man, woman">
    <meta name="description" content="if you want to give a life alternative to elderly peoples">
    <meta name="author" content="Wild Code School Developpers Group">
    <title>Adopt An Elderly</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../content/homestyle.css" media="all"/>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <h1 class="header-title">Adopt An Elderly</h1>
        <nav class="header-nav">
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#Concept">Concept</a></li>
                <li><a href="#Funniest Elderly">Funniest Elderly</a></li>
                <li><a href="#Get Your Elderly">Get Your Elderly</a></li>
                <li><a href="#Your Cart">Your Cart</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>                   
    </header>
    <div>
        <h2 id="Concept">Concept</h2>
        <p class="about-text">Nowadays, over a certain age, one of two elderly people ends up in a retirement home,
        where living conditions such as care, offered activities, and sociability are not optimal.<br>
        <br>"ADOPT AN ELDERLY" offers an alternative life for these people, and for you! <br><br>To welcome 
        these people at your home to benefit from their life experience, and to know that they will be 
        happier with you, this is what our site offers. Through your purchase from an elderly person, 
        we make donations to charities working for them all around the World. So don't wait any longer, do the good deed of your life!</p>
        <blockquote class="citation">
            <p>To care for those who once cared for us is one of the highest honors.</p>
        </blockquote>
        <div>
            <p class="blockquote-author">Tia Walker</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div>
        <h2 id="Funniest Elderly">Funniest Elderly</h2>
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Photo</th>
                    <th>Price</th>
                    <th>Name</th>
                    <th>Description</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
        @Each
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        @Current.Photo
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        @Current.Price
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        @Current.Name
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        @Current.Description
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        @EndEach
        </table>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <h2 id="Contact">Contact Us</h2>
        <form action="index.html">
                <p>Let's meet up</p>
                <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2639.8671619348547!2d7.762291315664368!3d48.57409297926072!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x4796c96d34025333%3A0x4fefbe61ce54f79a!2sWild%20Code%20School%20-%20Formation%20d%C3%A9veloppeur%20web!5e0!3m2!1sfr!2sfr!4v1572217476367!5m2!1sfr!2sfr" width="596" height="450" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>
                <p>For all your questions or requests for information<br>and your complaints, send us a message</p>
            <div class="labelblock">
                <label for="emailinput">Your Email</label>
                <input type="text" name="email" id="emailinput" placeholder="info@adoptanelderly.com">
            </div>
            <div class="labelblock">
                <label for="messageinput">Your Message</label>
                <input type="text" name="message" id="messageinput" placeholder="My message here">
            </div>
            <div class="labelblock">
                <input type="submit" value="Send" id="send-button">
            </div>
        </form>
        <div class="legal">
            <p>&copy; 2020 Adopt An Elderly -  All rights reserved - Made with ♥ by WildCodeSchoolDevGroups</p>
        </div>
      </footer>
